{{Top|canon=Chardaan Orbital Yards}}
The '''Chardaan Shipyards''' were a shipyard affiliated with the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]<ref name="CCG">{{CCG|set=Death Star II Limited|cardname=Green Squadron 1}}</ref> and the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].<ref name="DS">[[Darksaber (novel)|''Darksaber'']]</ref>

==History==
They produced many [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]], including [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|A-wings]], [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wings]], [[E-7 E-wing multi-role starfighter|E-wings]], [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]], and [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]].<ref name="DS" /> Some of their A-wings were used in the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].<ref name="CCG" /> The shipyards' structure included silver pressurized [[Hangar/Legends|hangar]] spheres.<ref name="DS" />

They were [[Battle of the Chardaan Shipyards|destroyed]] by [[Crimson Command]] under [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Ivan Cronus]] in [[12 ABY/Legends|12 ABY]].<ref name="DS" />

